  "concentration": false,
  "description": "Eight rays of light flash from you in a 60-foot Cone. Each creature in the Cone makes a Dexterity saving throw. For each target, roll 1d8 to determine which color ray affects it, consulting the Prismatic Rays table.\n\n@Embed[Compendium.dnd5e.tables24.RollTable.phbPrismaticRays rollable=true caption=false]{Prismatic Rays}",
  "duration": {
    "units": "inst",
    "value": null
  },
