    "supply": 0,
    "value": ""
  },
  "name": "Prismatic Spray",
  "passive_effects": [
    {
      "changes": [],
      "description": "<p>The target has the &amp;Reference[Restrained apply=false] condition and makes a [[/save ability=con format=long]] at the end of each of its turns. If it successfully saves three times, the condition ends. If it fails three times, it has the &amp;Reference[Petrified] condition until it is freed by an effect like the <em>@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.spells24.Item.phbsplGreaterRes]{Greater Restoration}</em> spell. The successes and failures needn\u2019t be consecutive; keep track of both until the target collects three of a kind.</p>",
      "disabled": false,
      "duration": null,
      "id": "cCQh7iXKnT8PKmc1",
      "name": "Petrifying (Indigo)",
      "statuses": [
        "restrained"
      ],
      "transfer": false
    },
    {
      "changes": [],
      "description": "<p>The target has the &amp;Reference[Blinded apply=false] condition and makes a [[/save ability=wis format=long]] at the start of your next turn. On a successful save, the condition ends. On a failed save, the condition ends, and the creature teleports to another plane of existence (DM\u2019s choice).</p>",
      "disabled": false,
      "duration": {
        "rounds": 1
      },
      "id": "jFAGct9YCYvLJodW",
      "name": "Teleporting (Violet)",
      "statuses": [
        "blinded"
      ],
      "transfer": false
    }
  ],
